'''帕爾默·費里曼·拉奇'''（{{lang-en|Palmer Freeman Luckey}}，{{bd|1992年|9月19日}}<ref name=redditbirthday/>）是[[歐酷拉|歐酷拉]]的原始創辦人，以及消費者[[虛擬實境|虛擬實境]][[頭戴式顯示器|頭戴式顯示器]][[Oculus_Rift|Oculus Rift]]的發明者。<ref name=oculusvr>{{cite web|title=People {{!}} Oculus Rift - Virtual Reality Headset for 3D Gaming|url=http://www.oculusvr.com/company/people/|publisher=Oculus VR|accessdate=2014-06-15|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140326134741/http://www.oculusvr.com/company/people/|archivedate=2014-03-26|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref name=grandpa /><ref name=corporaterecords />

== 早年生活 ==
拉奇生長於[[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]][[長灘_(加利福尼亞州)|長灘]]<ref name=latimes/>，家中成員有三位妹妹、<ref name=roadtovr>{{cite news|last1=Lang|first1=Ben|title=Q&A With Palmer Luckey, Creator of the Oculus Rift|url=http://www.roadtovr.com/palmer-luckey-oculus-rift-interview/|accessdate=2014-06-21|publisher=Road to VR|date=2012-10-16|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112003344/https://www.roadtovr.com/palmer-luckey-oculus-rift-interview/|dead-url=no}}</ref>母親和曾是汽車銷售員的父親。<ref name=eurogamer>{{cite news|last1=Purchese|first1=Robert|title=Happy Go Luckey: Meet the 20-year-old creator of Oculus Rift|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2013-07-11-happy-go-luckey-meet-the-20-year-old-creator-of-oculus-rift|accessdate=2014-06-15|publisher=Eurogamer.net|date=2013-07-11|archive-date=2021-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113193610/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2013-07-11-happy-go-luckey-meet-the-20-year-old-creator-of-oculus-rift|dead-url=no}}</ref>他幼年時在母親的教養下在家自學，曾上過帆船課程，<ref name=nypost/>且對電子有興趣。<ref name=grandpa/><ref name=wired/>他在14、15歲左右時至{{le|金西學院|Golden West College}}和{{le|長灘城市學院|Long Beach City College}}上社區大學課程。<ref name=roadtovr/>他在2009年成立了討論修正遊戲機和個人電腦等老舊硬體的網頁ModRetro論壇（ModRetro Forums）。<ref name=oculusvr/>之後於2010年開始在[[加州州立大學長灘分校|加州州立大學長灘分校]]就讀，<ref name=latimes/>主修的是新聞。<ref name=eurogamer/>在校期間，曾擔任該校其中一份學生經營報紙《Daily 49er》的在線編輯。<ref name="Daily 49er">{{cite web|url=http://www.daily49er.com/staff/?writer=Palmer%20Luckey|title=Daily 49er : Staff|publisher=Daily 49er|accessdate=2014-09-08|archive-date=2018-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181114224801/http://www.daily49er.com/staff/?writer=Palmer%20Luckey|dead-url=no}}</ref>

拉奇在11至16歲間便已經嘗試了各種的高電壓研究，其中包括[[線圈砲|線圈砲]]、[[特斯拉線圈|特斯拉線圈]]和[[雷射|雷射]]。<ref name=latimes/>更花費數萬美金，<ref name=wired>{{cite news|last1=Peckham|first1=Matt|title=The Inside Story of Oculus Rift and How Virtual Reality Became Reality|url=http://www.wired.com/2014/05/oculus-rift-4/|accessdate=2014-06-15|publisher=Wired|date=2014-05-20|archive-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118234136/https://www.wired.com/2014/05/oculus-rift-4/|dead-url=no}}</ref>以一個複雜的六顯示器的設置組成一部電腦。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Graham|first1=Jefferson|title=Talking Tech {{!}} The real world of Oculus VR founder Palmer Luckey|url=http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/video/talking-tech--the-real-world-of-oculus-vr-founder-palmer-luckey/3070090399001|accessdate=2014-06-19|publisher=USA TODAY|date=2014|archive-date=2016-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160424092908/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/video/talking-tech--the-real-world-of-oculus-vr-founder-palmer-luckey/3070090399001|dead-url=no}}</ref>拉奇靠著維修及轉售損壞的iPhone手機，也曾擔任帆船教練及維修船隻，賺取至少36,000美金來支撐他的研究。<ref name=roadtovr/>他對虛擬實境有著高度的興趣，並有著超過50款的頭戴式顯示器的龐大私人收藏，其中有一些是利用他所賺的錢，在拍賣會中以原始價格的一小部分購得。<ref name=latimes/><ref name=eurogamer/><ref name=wired/>

他在就讀加州州大期間，曾至[[南加州大學|南加州大學]]{{le|創造性技術研究院|Institute for Creative Technologies}}的混合實境研究室（MxR）<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://projects.ict.usc.edu/mxr/ |title=Mixed Reality Lab (MxR) |access-date=2014-11-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141121064806/http://projects.ict.usc.edu/mxr/ |archive-date=2014-11-21 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>擔任工程師，作為找出使虛擬實境具有成本效益的設計團隊。<ref name=latimes/><ref name=oculusvr/>

